{"questionId":"9076874","questionHtml":"<p>A beam of monochromatic light is incident normally on a diffraction grating. The grating spacing is <em>d</em>.&nbsp;The angles between the different orders are shown on the diagram.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"><img src=\"__IMG__/84421fb9c4058bf621b50a0f75dfa02315db32d1.png\"></p>\n<p>What is the expression for the wavelength of light used?</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>A.&nbsp; &nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\frac{{d\\,{\\text{sin}}\\,\\alpha }}{2}\">\n  <mfrac>\n    <mrow>\n      <mi>d</mi>\n      <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n      <mrow>\n        <mtext>sin</mtext>\n      </mrow>\n      <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n      <mi>α</mi>\n    </mrow>\n    <mn>2</mn>\n  </mfrac>\n</math></span></p>\n<p>B.&nbsp; &nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\frac{{d\\,{\\text{sin}}\\,\\beta }}{2}\">\n  <mfrac>\n    <mrow>\n      <mi>d</mi>\n      <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n      <mrow>\n        <mtext>sin</mtext>\n      </mrow>\n      <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n      <mi>β</mi>\n    </mrow>\n    <mn>2</mn>\n  </mfrac>\n</math></span></p>\n<p>C.&nbsp; &nbsp;<em>d</em> sin&nbsp;α</p>\n<p>D.&nbsp; &nbsp;<em>d</em>&nbsp;sin β</p>","markschemeHtml":"<p>B</p>","meta":{"questionId":"9076874","referenceCode":"18N.1.HL.TZ0.28","subjectId":"46-dp-physics-last-assessment-2024","title":"A beam of monochromatic light is incident normally on a diffraction grating. The grating spacing is d. The angles between the different orders are shown on the diagram. What is the","paper":"1","level":"HL","questionNumber":"28","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 1]","breadcrumbLabels":["Additional higher level (AHL)","Additional higher level (AHL)","Topic 9: Wave phenomena","9.3 – Interference","Additional higher level (AHL)","Topic 9: Wave phenomena"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}}}